config MTK_GPT_SCHEME_SUPPORT
	bool "MTK GPT SCHEME SUPPORT"
	help
	  GPT is GUID Partition Table
	  MTK driver support gpt scheme layout
	  GPT is a better partition layout scheme
	  GPT is instead of PMT

